# C++ library with a bundled CLI - full project. A reusable static library (public API
# under include/) plus a thin app/ binary that links it. Combines the library tier's API
# split with the application tier's release machinery: because it ships a distributable
# binary it keeps the functional test layer, the Docker release matrix and workflows-app,
# which cpp-lib does not have. All three test layers apply. Use cpp-lib when there is no
# binary to ship, cpp-app when there is no reusable library behind a public API.
